title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1987-06-20
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, Franklin's Tower, Minglewood Blues, Loser, My Brother Esau, Bird Song

Set 2

Iko Iko, Looks Like Rain, Deal, Drums, Gimme Some Lovin', All Along The Watchtower, The Wheel, The Other One, Wharf Rat, Sugar Magnolia, E: One More Saturday Night

premier of All Along The Watchtower

reviews.review_text: Summer '87~ To my ears, this is by far the cleanest sounding AUD of this show.  Nice work here bitz~
